## Limitations

The findings are based on publicly available information and may not cover all possible barriers to collective learning. The sources used are primarily from online platforms, which may not always provide peer-reviewed or academically rigorous content. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of technology and information dissemination means that new barriers may emerge that are not covered in this report.